## Review cadence

- **Weekly:** CoS runs the strategic-plan health check (see
  `docs/StrategicPlanning.md` §5.4). Surfaces drift at any layer.
- **Monthly:** {{OWNER_NAME}} reviews `Goals.md` itself —
  reprioritize Interim Goals, churn Initiatives.
- **Quarterly:** Strategic review — are the Outcomes still the
  right ones? Are the Interim Goals proving predictive?

